data_table.description: Cognitive Function Form, Exam 2. Participants with or without atherosclerosis and cardiovascular disease and involved in the "Atherosclerosis Risk in Communities (ARIC) Cohort" project.

variable.name: CNFAFLAG
variable.description: =1 if form is present [Cognitive Function Form, exam 2]
